    List of shortcuts:
    F1        Help
    ` 1 2 3 4 (top row) RGB/R/G/B/A
    0 - =     (top row) Exposure Reset/EV-/EV+
    R         Adjust Gain and Offset to fit Range
    [         Next AOV
    ]         Previous AOV
    PgUp PgDn Next/Previous MIP
    F         Fit/100%
    I         Inspect Tool
    F5        Reload image
    F11       Fullscreen
    H         Hide UI
    + -       (numpad) ZoomIn/ZoomOut
    Esc       Exit
